sub_title: Cultural Studies, Performance Studies, Entertainment Production, Consumer Behavior and Promotional Strategies
summary:
Strong educational background in Media Communications, Cultural Studies and Performance Studies, with developed knowledge in Journalism and Political Sciences. Solid multicultural experience and understanding, with a passion for cooking and puppies ^.^

Let your work become a passion, it will bring you the fulfillment you seek! Also,  don't forget to love your food and love your puppies ^.^
